{"tid":1545974,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"831 我要太子死嘅手足名留千史！","createTime":"2019-09-06T06:06:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T14:41:10.000Z","uid":113155,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"54d31066586521e17968dd56e53d742e87c5e73c","tid":1545974,"uid":113155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T06:06:01.000Z","msg":"整合：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">黨鐵暫時唔刪片</span></strong></span>，我覺得如果出人命，黨鐵唔會夠僵刪。<br />\n毛ee : 港鐵會keep住831 CCTV到無需要再用為止<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1545686\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1545686</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n張超雄：港鐵已將8月31日太子站閉路電視片段根據程予和指引保留<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1545685\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1545685</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我哋可以做咩：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">文宣叫831當時站內嘅人企出黎告黑警！咁就可以拎片啦！<br />\n</span></strong></span><br />\n例子：黑警搞到我情緒困擾，唔敢搭地鐵！我要告一哥！<br />\n告佢老母！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n參考：<br />\n報稱太子站警打人致情緒困擾　前法庭書記向一哥申索<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190903/mobile/bkn-20190903180209006-0903_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190903%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190903180209006-0903_00822_001.html&d=qjQisgq6tteJ1Wb%2FuF84H0zKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=cc8de5ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190903/mobile/bkn-20190903180209006-0903_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[法律] [一石二鳥] 教你點攞法庭命令迫黨鐵交太子站CCTV 再告埋香港警察同港鐵！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1534194\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1534194</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n黑警打死嘅第一個手足，唔可以備佢當失蹤人口咁籍籍無名，白白犠牺！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我要佢喺給香港歷史上有名有姓，名留千史！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8ed12b17a70ac77751ce096127bfe54a48018d5","tid":1545974,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T06:06:23.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c5620e1c84153d286abfbf732e1c202d6a7d88b9","tid":1545974,"uid":113155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T06:06:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qq1cmDx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQq1cmDx.png&h=6b2dee90&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f3237b2cf26052c7948d0e92ed08d9f5b9cb4333","tid":1545974,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T06:06:45.000Z","msg":"7/9機場更新 求求大家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1545323\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1545323</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/suRLDoM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsuRLDoM.png&h=b3f794e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=qjQisgq6tteJ1Wb%2FuF84H0zKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=284143b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"ce090bea4ffdb701024d7481bd12ce2506d6639b","tid":1545974,"uid":24465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T06:06:50.000Z","msg":"大家9月8